Compile and run :
1)To compile: make (or make clean and then make preferably, *requires libao and mpg123 libraries.)
2)Then do ./sample2D to start the game


Controls : 
1) press A or D to move the cannon up or down
2) press S or F to rotate the cannon
3) press CTRL + left CTRL + right to move blue basket
4) press ALT + left ALT + right to move red basket
5) press space bar to shoot a cannon
6) speed can be increased by N and decreased by M 


Scoring : 
1) shooting red/ blue woud yeild -1 point
2) shooting black would yield +1 point
3) if red goes in red basket, you get +1, and the same holds for blue

